nodes.text: The Doshian jellyfish was a type of jellyfish from the planet Trandosha. The claws of the sentient Trandoshan species could cut and flay wroshyr wood as easily as a they could a Doshian jellyfish.

Doshian jellyfishes were mentioned in "Tooth and Claw", a short story written by Michael Kogge and published in the From a Certain Point of View: The Empire Strikes Back anthology in 2020. They originally appeared in 2005 as a hologram in the Star Wars Legends video game Star Wars Galaxies: Rage of the Wookiees.
